title: Version 0.6.0
message: Version 0.6.0

title: Add new preference minimum notification priority
message: Add new preference minimum notification priority

title: Put startGenerate method in KeyGeneratorService
message:
Put startGenerate method in KeyGeneratorService

Because it could be easy too miss manually setting currentlyGenerating
variable otherwise

That variable need to be set instantly to avoid starting generating
multiple times

It should not be set inside the service (onHandleIntent()) because
that runs on a different thread and there is some delay before it starts

title: Dont expect to read zero or less bytes
message: Dont expect to read zero or less bytes

title: Throw RuntimeException if value is less than zero
message:
Throw RuntimeException if value is less than zero

Value may be zero if for example a notification title is an empty string
then the length of that string will be zero

This is an unsigned operation because a value less than zero is never
expected

title: Fix bug that caused AN2Linux to crash
message:
Fix bug that caused AN2Linux to crash

Was using Fragment#getContext() which was added in Android api 23

Android studio usually warns when using something that is not available
in minSdkVersion but apparently not for getContext()

title: Add new preference for local only notifications
message:
Add new preference for local only notifications

This is available from API_20+.
Before this AN2Linux blocked all notifications flagged as local only.
Now let user decide instead.

title: Fix bug that made an2linux unusable on kitkat
message:
Fix bug that made an2linux unusable on kitkat

Was trying to use unsupported ciphers for android kitkat users

Also needed to change a little in the implementation for SSLEngine,
apparantly it works differently on api 19

For example with api 19 it needs to do multiple unwrap but on api 23
one unwrap was necessary
